'''Mythcon 35''' was the thirty-fifth annual [[Mythopoeic Society]] conference.

*'''Theme:''' "Bridges to Other Worlds: Thirty-Five Years of Mythopoeic Scholarship"
*'''Guests of Honor:''' Charles Huttar (Charles Williams scholar) and Neil Gaiman (fantasy author)
*'''Chairman:''' Marion Van Loo and Judith Kollmann
